data.description: What a great opportunity to get a waterfront property on Berry lake.  The channel behind the house leads to the main lake.  This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home is as cute as can be.  Its fully functional for a single person or a couple. The main living area has an open concept kitchen, dining area and living room.  A small gas fireplace and electric baseboard heat in the bedrooms is all it takes to keep it toasty and comfortable without breaking the bank.  All appliances will be included.  there are three sizeable sheds for all of the lake toys, mower and other equipment needed.  There are no HOA fees either.  Come on out and take a look at what this little investment can buy you.  All information is believed to be true at time of listing, but should be verified by agent and buyer themselves.
